  "intro": "<p> </p>\n\n<p class=\"f-brk\" style=\"margin-top: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px;\">又是一年花开暖春之季，曾经陪在你身边的那个人还在吗？</p>\n\n<p class=\"f-brk\" style=\"margin-top: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px;\">《陪在你身边》是毛泽少作词作曲的暖心之作，在这个绽放的季节 散发着怀恋，我的心很甜，有了你不再左顾右盼。</p>\n\n<p class=\"f-brk\" style=\"margin-top: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px;\"> </p>\n\n<p class=\"f-brk\" style=\"margin-top: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px;\">就让我陪在你的身边</p>\n\n<p class=\"f-brk\" style=\"margin-top: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px;\">陪你去看世界</p>\n\n<p class=\"f-brk\" style=\"margin-top: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px;\">大大小小的风景</p>\n\n<p class=\"f-brk\" style=\"margin-top: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px;\">全部收进相册纪念</p>\n\n<p class=\"f-brk\" style=\"margin-top: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px;\">就让我陪在你的身边</p>\n\n<p class=\"f-brk\" style=\"margin-top: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px;\">直到青春飞远</p>\n\n<p class=\"f-brk\" style=\"margin-top: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px;\">也不枉费这一辈子的羁绊</p>\n\n<p class=\"f-brk\" style=\"margin-top: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px;\">陪在你身边</p>\n\n<p class=\"f-brk\" style=\"margin-top: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px;\"> </p>\n\n<p class=\"f-brk\" style=\"margin-top: 4px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px;\">时过境迁，陪在你身边的人不论是他还是她，抓住眼前的这个人，一起去看世界，去哪里不重要，重要的是有这么一个人，一直陪在你身边。</p>\n    \n<p> </p>",
